      "updated": 1771901657420,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "electron/main.ts         App entry, window management, registers all 13 handler groups\nelectron/db.ts           PrismaClient singleton (getDb() / disconnectDb())\nelectron/logger.ts       Logging utility\nelectron/ipc/            13 domain handler files (see Zone 2)\n\nIn-memory:  activeSessions Map  (holds live conversation state per session)\nPattern:    Handler calls core/ functions → writes results to DB via Prisma",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "electron/main.ts         App entry, window management, registers all 13 handler groups\nelectron/db.ts           PrismaClient singleton (getDb() / disconnectDb())\nelectron/logger.ts       Logging utility\nelectron/ipc/            13 domain handler files (see Zone 2)\n\nIn-memory:  activeSessions Map  (holds live conversation state per session)\nPattern:    Handler calls core/ functions → writes results to DB via Prisma",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
