    {
      "id": "elem_192_417beaa8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 72,
      "y": 3366,
      "width": 505.64,
      "height": 249.70000000000002,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "elem_188_02a2b9c0"
      ],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771901657422,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Triggered: after each conversation session or on daily app open\n\n 1. tom.runAnalysis() IPC → electron/ipc/tom.ts\n 2. Fetch all items (journeyman+), recent sessions, recent reviews\n 3. → core/tom: detectAvoidance(items, sessions)\n 4. → core/tom: detectConfusionPairs(errors across sessions)\n 5. → core/tom: detectRegression(items, recentReviews)\n 6. → core/tom: detectModalityGap(items)\n 7. UPSERT TomInference rows (create new / update existing)\n 8. Mark resolved inferences as resolved=true\n 9. generateExpandedDailyBrief(allInferences)\n10. Return ExpandedTomBrief (consumed by conversation planner)\n\nOutput feeds directly into Flow B, step 3.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Triggered: after each conversation session or on daily app open\n\n 1. tom.runAnalysis() IPC → electron/ipc/tom.ts\n 2. Fetch all items (journeyman+), recent sessions, recent reviews\n 3. → core/tom: detectAvoidance(items, sessions)\n 4. → core/tom: detectConfusionPairs(errors across sessions)\n 5. → core/tom: detectRegression(items, recentReviews)\n 6. → core/tom: detectModalityGap(items)\n 7. UPSERT TomInference rows (create new / update existing)\n 8. Mark resolved inferences as resolved=true\n 9. generateExpandedDailyBrief(allInferences)\n10. Return ExpandedTomBrief (consumed by conversation planner)\n\nOutput feeds directly into Flow B, step 3.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
