      "updated": 1771901657422,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. src/ NEVER imports from\n   electron/ or core/\n   (all access via IPC)\n\n2. core/ has ZERO deps on\n   Electron, React, or Prisma\n   (pure functions only)\n\n3. electron/ipc/ is the ONLY\n   layer that touches Prisma\n\n4. shared/types.ts is the ONLY\n   file importable everywhere",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. src/ NEVER imports from\n   electron/ or core/\n   (all access via IPC)\n\n2. core/ has ZERO deps on\n   Electron, React, or Prisma\n   (pure functions only)\n\n3. electron/ipc/ is the ONLY\n   layer that touches Prisma\n\n4. shared/types.ts is the ONLY\n   file importable everywhere",
      "autoResize": true,
